description: Get the Professional Listings to determine the listing or avoid receiving penalty points

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: Partner API assigned user registration is successful, Required for all requests.

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is a UNIX timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes.

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id and path frequency limiting algorithm. More details.

parameters.name: page_no
parameters.description: Specifies the page number of data to return in the result set. For page >0, an empty array will be returned when no more data.

parameters.name: page_size
parameters.description: Each result set is returned as a page of records. Use this to specify the page size of data to return in the result set. This integer value is used to specify the maximum number of orders to return in a result set.

response_fields.name: code
response_fields.description: Indicate error status first time. Empty for success.

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error detail first time. Empty for success.

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: Tag identify for per API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: reason
response_fields.description: Reason of no item. Applicable values: 1. Cancelled 2. Deleted 3. Censored 4. Inappropriate Price 5. Sold (shop Unavailable) 6. Not visible (temporarily)

response_fields.name: total_count
response_fields.description: Total number of listing with scores
